/p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/self-esteem-declares-i-deserve-to-be-here-on-focus-is-power-from-new-album-a-complicated-woman-3830836">新专辑“A Complicated Woman”中的“Focus Is Power”中的“自尊”帖子宣称“我值得在这里”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
